    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普实施较温和的关税，亚洲债券将落后于新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-bonds-to-trail-em-peers-if-trump-enacts-milder-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果唐纳德·特朗普的关税政策比人们担心的更为温和，新兴亚洲债券的价格将变得更加昂贵，其吸引力将低于全球同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-bonds-to-trail-em-peers-if-trump-enacts-milder-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>托克集团认为陷入困境的碳信用市场将迎来反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/trafigura-bets-troubled-carbon-credits-market-poised-for-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大宗商品交易巨头托克集团 (Trafigura Group) 有望在陷入困境的碳信用市场实现创纪录的增长，因为它认为新的监管框架将推动碳信用工具成为排放核算的主流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/trafigura-bets-troubled-carbon-credits-market-poised-for-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
